FoodContainer

Class JellyMeat

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game.Food
      • FoodContainer.JellyMeat

  • public class JellyMeat
extends Food
    The JellyMeat Class is for creating a food of type JellyMeat it inherits its methods from the abstract class Food.

    The class defines the Jelly Meat's food name, price and nutritional value. The class is needed to create multiple Jelly Meat's of type Food which can then be brought from a shop at the set price and then eaten for the set nutritional value.

    Author:
    Jade Martin, Kyran Stagg
